This package uses quilt as patch system. Please, refer to
/usr/share/doc/quilt/README.source for more about adding, removing or
updating the patches on this package.

Also, "dpkg-source --commit" might work well for adding smaller fixes.

To incorporate new upstream releases: gbp import-orig --uscan

To generate desktop files for new hacks, use debian/screensavers-desktop-qa.sh

This package is uploaded using dgit, please consider using it for your uploads.
